parameters: ...The shrine at night is scary, isn't it?
Ghost: Ah, you...! Can you see me?!
Um... There have been various things happening.

Ghost: Hey, please! I want you to help me find
peace!

Ghost: Thank you for listening. My name is Mina.
Nice to meet you.
Oh, a ghost, but you seem like a decent person.

My name is Ayako. So, what can I do to help you
find peace, Mina-san?

Mina: ...Before we get into the main topic, can I
ask you something?... It's really embarrassing,
but the cause of my death was... excessive
masturbation...

Eh...?! I-If you masturbate too much, do you
really die?! That's... that's...

Mina: ...Your concerns seem different, but oh
well.

Mina: I don't really have any hobbies, so when it
comes to relieving stress, the only method I had
was masturbation.

Mina: Especially on days when I was exhausted from
work, I had a habit of borrowing AV and
masturbating alone until I fell asleep.

Mina: ...And on that day, I was able to find and
borrow an extremely rare video that is said to be
a legend among enthusiasts!

Mina: I thought of making it the main course and
having 10 videos as appetizers for my masturbation
session...!... But that became the trigger for a
tragedy.

Having 10 appetizers... that's a harsh
masturbation session, isn't it?

Mina: ...My body was worn out from consecutive
all-nighters and an unhealthy diet... My heart was
pounding so hard with anticipation for the
legendary AV...

Mina: After finishing watching the 10th video,
just before \.\....., I experienced an intense
climax and my heart stopped...

(This might be the scariest story I've ever
heard... I should be careful too...)

Mina: And after I died, the police confiscated all
the videos and stored them in a warehouse!! So, no
one can sneak a peek at them by playing them...!

Mina: I... I...! Ugh... I regret more than
anything that I died without being able to watch
the legendary AV... Ugh... Ugh...

I understand the story... even though I can't
comprehend it.

Mina: I have all the details and synopsis of that
AV in my head! But, I probably won't be able to
get my hands on it anymore...

Mina: That's why I want you to recreate the same
project!!
R-Recreation?! Are you telling me to have sex?!

Mina: I get more excited by the buildup rather
than the actual act!! You don't have to go that
far, it's okay.

Mina: Please...! I can't have any regrets in the
next life like this...!! Please... give me a
chance....!

I-If you're going to say it like that... B-But! I
won't have sex, okay!

Mina: Ah, Ayako-san...!!! Thank you so much...
Ugh... Really... Thank you... Ugh... Ugh...
So? What is the content of that?

Ghost: Ah! It's not Ayako-san. Please!! Just one
more time, stay with me!

Ghost: Ayako-san...! Just one more time...! Please
give me one more chance...! I beg you!
Will you give me a chance?
